clusterList.phrase: try not to edit what you say too much today to anyone you shouldn't say everything that comes to mind but you should be more open you will get what you want much quicker if you speak honestly and from the heart whether you are in the business situation at school or cuddling with your sweetie you need to be frank and even a little bit vulnerable people can tell when you're being genuine and it goes a long way toward making a really significant connection
